    {
      "id": 11,
      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "### \ud83e\udde0 Autonomous Agent Pipeline \u2014 `$agent_service`\nThree-agent flow: **Triage** \u2192 **Investigate** (MCP ReAct loop) \u2192 **Remediate**. Span names: `sre_agent.triage`, `sre_agent.investigation`, `sre_agent.remediation`.",
        "background_color": "purple",
        "font_size": "14",
        "text_align": "left",
        "vertical_align": "center",
        "show_tick": false,
        "tick_pos": "50%",
        "tick_edge": "left",
        "has_padding": true
