      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "### \u26a1 Bedrock & LLM Observability\nBedrock **Converse** calls are wrapped as explicit `llm` spans (model, input/output, token usage). Token usage, **cost**, evaluations (`rca_quality`, `confidence_score`), and the full agent trace (`workflow` \u2192 `llm` \u2192 `tool`) live in **AI Observability \u2192 Traces** \u2014 filter `ml_app:sre-agent-ecs`. Charts below are APM trace metrics.",
        "background_color": "orange",
        "font_size": "14",
        "text_align": "left",
        "vertical_align": "center",
        "show_tick": false,
